            <title>AYANEO Pocket S2 系列安卓掌机发布：首发第三代骁龙 G3、8000mAh 起步电池，预订价 2999 元起</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/861/957.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/861/957.htm</guid>
